    <note>Xie(1) Bi [732] Chen(1) Zhizhong's [34] father-in-law. Affinal relation of Wei(5) Yu [1949]. The 27th generation descendant of the Jin dynasty Taifu, Xie(1) An [3365], whose family's ancestral home was Yangxia, the origin of the Chenjun (or Chenliu jun) Xie(1). His great granddaughter was Tan(3) Shan's [1587] wife. At some point, his descendants moved to Yingzhou, Ruyin xian. Zheng Xia, WJ, 4.3a; Zhou Jiamou, Nanbei shibiao (CSJC ed.), 1.130, 133; XCB, 33.6a, 7a, 34.1a, 55.12a; Xinan zhi, 6.16a; SS, 306.1a-2b. CBD, 5, 4100-1.</note>
